      "id": "f4107f07fbea4245",
      "text": "What one does, if one \"uses\" such bombs, is not annihilation but extermination. What is new is not only the possibility of man's self-annihilation. With the possibility of a lightning extermination of millions, a new power of injury has arisen, a new power of killing, indeed a new act of killing, a human act of a new kind."
